OL,3,CWoman to get life-saving surgery after
OL,4,Cgenerosity of strangers
OL,6,FITV Granada Reports journalist Mel
OL,7,FBarham spoke to Lauren about the
OL,8,Fastonishing act of genorosity that
OL,9,Fcould change her life forever.
OL,11,FThe family of a woman who has a rare
OL,12,Fcondition which means her jaw is
OL,13,Flocked shut are celebrating after
OL,14,Fstrangers helped them raise thousands
OL,15,Ffor life-changing surgery.
OL,17,FLauren Bolton, from Rossendale,
OL,18,FLancashire, lives in constant pain and
OL,19,Fis unable to eat solid food.
