OL,3,CWoman to get life-saving surgery after
OL,4,Cgenerosity of strangers
OL,6,FWithout urgent surgery her family fear
OL,7,Fher health will continue to
OL,8,Fdeteriorate.
OL,10,FIn a last-ditch attempt the 29-year-
OL,11,Fold's family set up a in the hope of
OL,12,Fraising money for private surgery to
OL,13,Freplace her jaw joint - which prompted
OL,14,Fa local businessman to step forward
OL,15,Fand offer help.
OL,17,FThe anonymous man told Lauren if she
OL,18,Fcould raise just over half the #95,000
OL,19,Fneeded for the surgery, he would
OL,20,Fdonate the rest.
