OL,6,FAfter describing the impact of the ,
OL,7,FLauren then watched as donations
OL,8,Fincreased to #61,000 in just a few
OL,9,Fdays.
OL,11,FLauren said: "I'm just blown away with
OL,12,Feveryone's kindness. Everyone who
OL,13,Fshared, everyone who's messaged. I've
OL,14,Fread those messages more than once."
OL,16,FThe local businessman reached out to
OL,17,FLauren's father, Paul Bolton, to help.
OL,19,FPaul said: "He just said they'd sat
OL,20,Fthere and watched it and he said he
OL,21,Fwas really touched by our story.
