OL,3,CWoman to get life-saving surgery after
OL,4,Cgenerosity of strangers
OL,6,FShe said: "It's actually starting to
OL,7,Ffeel real now that I might not be
OL,8,Fliving like this for the next four
OL,9,Fyears.
OL,11,F"For so long, my life has been on
OL,12,Fhold. I have not been able to plan
OL,13,Fahead... To get this surgery would
OL,14,Fjust open so many doors."
OL,16,FSince ITV Granada's report on Lauren's
OL,17,Fcondition, she's received money and
OL,18,Fsupport both online, in person, and
OL,19,Feven through the post.
